Package com.complexible.common.protobuf.io

Interface Summary
ProtobufDataInput<T extends MessageLite> A DataInput which can also read protobuf messages.
ProtobufDataOutput A DataOutput which knows how to write protobuf messages.
ProtobufReader<T extends MessageLite> Interface for reading protobuf messages from some source.
ProtobufWriter Interface for writing Protobuf messages to some output.
 

Class Summary
InputStreamRawProtobufReader<T extends MessageLite> Implementation of a ProtobufReader which will read Protobuf messages from an InputStream.
InputStreamSizeDelimitedProtobufReader<T extends MessageLite> Implementation of a ProtobufReader which will read Protobuf messages from an InputStream.
OutputStreamProtobufWriter Implementation of ProtobufWriter which will write protobuf message to an output stream.
Protobuf Utility class for protobuf IO
